9421 };
9422
9423 // Emit the opcode for the instruction.
9424 uint64_t Bits = 0;
9425 Bits |= (uint64_t)OpInfo0[MI->getOpcode()] << 0;
9426 Bits |= (uint64_t)OpInfo1[MI->getOpcode()] << 32;
9427 Bits |= (uint64_t)OpInfo2[MI->getOpcode()] << 48;
9428 return {AsmStrs+(Bits & 2047)-1, Bits};
9429
9430}

9432/// from the instruction set description.

21219 }
21220 } while (AsmString[I] != '\0');
21221 }
21222
21223 return true;
21224}
